1. First download xampp from here byt selecting appropriate platform: https://www.apachefriends.org/download.html
2. Rename the downloaded file to "myXampp.run" for simplicity.
3. Then run these set of commands:

    chmod 755 myXampp.run
    sudo ./myXampp.run
   
4. Then use xampp_start and xampp_stop for starting stopping xampp which are already there in MyScripts.
